  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Job description</p><ul><li>Ensure stocks are updated in a timely manner.</li><li>Assists in department daily routine.</li><li>Perform good customer service.</li><li>Perform stock control and follow up on office maintenance.</li><li>Pack and prepare stocks for delivery.</li><li>Ad hoc duties that are assigned from time to time.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Entry level candidates are welcome</li><li>Minimum GCE 'O' Levels or ITE / Diploma / Professional Certification in Administration are welcome to apply.</li><li>Willing to learn with good attitude.</li><li>Organized and responsible.</li><li>Salary will be commensurate based on experience and qualifications.</li></ul>",
